Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Slimmer social security
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wzvn
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 24 Apr 1983
President Reagan signs new social security bill despite his original claims of harder cuts. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less